QuestData.Title: Indecipherable Map
QuestData.Description:
<The map is covered in scribbles and notations that hint at realms unknown.
Ve'nari would likely find this fascinating.>
QuestData.LogDescription: Bring the Indecipherable Map to Ve'nari at Ve'nari's Refuge.
QuestData.RewardText:
<Ve'nari raises the map, inspecting it closely.>
And these stains--you said they were here when you found it?
